headline: Markem-Imaje Launches Ultraply Range of Print and Apply Consumables Catering to Scannable 2D Barcode Demand
summary: Markem-Imaje, part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a global provider of end-to-end supply chain solutions and industrial marking and coding systems, today announced the launch of its Ultraply ribbons and self-adhesive labels range. With its innovative Print and Apply (P&A) labelers, the new range addresses growing demand for high-quality, phone scannable 2D barcodes driven by the exponential rise of e-commerce and direct-to-consumer (DTC) models.
